content: I am currently volunteering for the 4pm phone bank. I have encountered several that are saying that they are not a democrat or will never vote for a democrat. But these individusals didn't specifically say they are a trump supporter. If I follow the script, I am just clicking 'other'? This seems like it is not the ideal way to share what happened on the phone call. Please advise.
If all they offer is they won't vote democrat then "Other" is the correct choice.
